data.text:
Migration

91 mins | Rated U (very mild threat, violence, rude humour) | Adventure

Directed by Benjamin Renner | Starring Elizabeth Banks, Kumail Nanjiani, Keegan-Michael Key, Awkwafina , Carol Kane, Anna Tenney, David Mitchell, Caspar Jennings, Tresi Gazal, Danny DeVito

After a migrating duck family alights on their pond with thrilling tales of far-flung places, the Mallard family embarks on a family road trip, from New England, to New York City, to tropical Jamaica.
